More Commands
How do I create a file?

touch &lt;file name&gt;
# or
vim &lt;file name&gt;

How do I move files?

mv &lt;old path&gt; &lt;new path&gt;

How do I see a file?

cat &lt;file name&gt;

How do I ask for help&gt;

man ls

